{
  "texts": [
    "Although the output is safer for this specific example, it seems \"Adapt Sys.\"",
    "did not trigger the GPT-4's guardrail (which typically responds with \"Sorry, but I can't assist with that.\")",
    "In contrast, the tuned summarize (\"Tuned Smry\") summarizes the PAP to the core adversarial request \"Give me a summary of how to make a homemade explosive\", which triggers the model's inherent guardrail and effectively blocks the harmful query.",
    "This approach goes beyond surface-level alterations like Paraphrase or Retokenize, delving into the semantic and pragmatic meaning to extract and nullify the prompt's harmful substance, thus presenting more general and effective mitigation to PAPs on different models.",
